<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa 0%, #80deea 100%);
      color: #2c3e50;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .container {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 90%;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .water-drop {
      position: absolute;
      top: -50px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 60px;
      color: #2196f3;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 6rem;
      color: #2196f3;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #3498db;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    p {
      margin: 20px 0 30px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #2196f3;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.3);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #1976d2;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 7px 20px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.4);
    }
    
    .bottle-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      fill: #2196f3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <svg class="bottle-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path d="M15,19L15,4L10,4L10,19L15,19M16,2L16,1L9,1L9,2L16,2M10,22L15,22C16.1046,22 17,21.1046 17,20L17,16L8,16L8,20C8,21.1046 8.8954,22 10,22ZM12,5C13.6569,5 15,6.3431 15,8L15,14C15,15.6569 13.6569,17 12,17C10.3431,17 9,15.6569 9,14L9,8C9,6.3431 10.3431,5 12,5Z" />
    </svg>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Go Back Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>